Content.Title: Testing2
Content.BodyCopy:
How to Complete and Submit Testing Center Forms using Firefox Version 19

1. Select the desired form link on our website. (http://www.byui.edu/testing-services/faculty-testing-help)

2. The form will open with a light yellow bar across the top.  Select the "Open With Different Viewer" button.

1. Select the "Open with Adobe Acrobat (default) button.  (If you would like to ALWAYS open PDF documents this way, check the "Do this automatically for files like this from now on" box.)

2. Select "OK."

1.       Complete the form and submit it.
